It's Showtime A-Holes! Grab your Zargnuts and jet packs and join us for the final adventure in James Gunn's GOTG series, Guardians of the Galaxy Vol 3! With enough heart, humor, and spectacle to make a grown man cry, Vol 3 is jam-packed with call backs, flashbacks, and even some surprises as we say goodbye to one of the best teams in cinema history. Get on board with this super deep dive into the themes, arc and storytelling techniques that will make this film one for the ages!

If you can, please leave us a review on [ITunes](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by ComicBook Clique, the only stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.

Send us feedback at ComicBookClique@Gmail.com! You Are Worthy! 

